{"tid":2159604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【基本法】第69條 立法會 每屆任期四年。大狀黨如何認同臨立會立憲？","createTime":"2020-08-16T12:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:52:42.000Z","uid":289191,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fae8702addd7e1fdf6798eaf5c81c2f3c3bf22e","tid":2159604,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"<em>《基本法》第六十九條<br />\n香港特別行政區立法會除第一屆任期為兩年外，每屆任期四年。</em><br />\n<br />\n人大常委的決定是赤裸裸違反第69條，<br />\n如果公民黨民主黨接受任命，<br />\n即是承認人大常委可以違反基本法<br />\n這不是解釋或僭建，<br />\n而是絕對，白紙黑字地違反。<br />\n<br />\n支持入臨立會的梁家傑，何俊仁，涂瑾申不是律師嗎？<br />\n今後人大常委為所欲為，這些人渣都是幫凶，是歷史罪人。"},{"pid":"d015251d76a94710a3981ee6b080bcb83eb925e0","tid":2159604,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"急！請科勞袁弓夷TWITTER<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159605</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a43086d1b28cb4a944aaf93f011c335f5ce0543c","tid":2159604,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67b51a4b12c88d395c4dd0dc247d14a92e3447b2","tid":2159604,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a43086d1b28cb4a944aaf93f011c335f5ce0543c","tid":2159604,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"THANKS"},{"pid":"62adde7d5539f66084142b866c718c0c110b5ffe","tid":2159604,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"公民黨還有資格捍衛法治嗎？"},{"pid":"42aa68662e770f53977d3bfcb1fa7f4934b78073","tid":2159604,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"從今以後，偽民主派批評支共違反基本法時，<br />\n支共會答：2020年臨立會果次你又唔嘈？"},{"pid":"0ff452afb013961c40f9ad938861950b9cf45884","tid":2159604,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi